      <title>२०६ पाण्डव-निवर्तनम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/01_Adiparva/14_vidurAgamanarAjyalambhaparva/02_rAjyalAbhaH/206_pANDava-nivartanam/</link>
